dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.globalconstraints

Interface IPhysConstrs

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IPhysConstrs
extends IEntity
    IPhysConstrs: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents the ability to express physical constraints. Therefore it has (in opposite to InternalConstrs) a reference to a Unit.
